          "params": [],
          "returnType": null,
          "description": "Reserved TileLayer.properties key holding the JSON-encoded raw IntGrid CSV array (readonly number[]) for a TileLayer converted from an LDtk IntGrid layer instance. Index = y * layer.width + x; 0 = empty. Prefer getLdtkIntGridValueAt over reading this directly."
        },
